{"tid":2097233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你地會唔會拎鹽拿痱滋？","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T16:35:24.000Z","uid":250594,"like":47,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6acb9563fd34754a75f17d0a0db75151a9bec1a0","tid":2097233,"uid":250594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"成日聽人話生痱滋拎鹽拿下會快啲好，我一直都有咁做覺得無咩事。但上次search見到有人話咁其實唔好會仲難好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到庭拎鹽拿痱滋嘅傳聞有冇野證實到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會拎鹽拿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太痛不了<br />\n<br />\nps生痱滋真係好煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想好好咁食野"},{"pid":"cf598b34efed2ac3199b829aae608cb35c077794","tid":2097233,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"用開西瓜霜或者唔知咩口內炎軟膏"},{"pid":"d49c4a9fe2903b70b7e660723e51d47a2ef56b34","tid":2097233,"uid":1524,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70aaaa9caa44b8a4cdaac67c21b18736879a46fe","tid":2097233,"uid":172454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"通常等佢發咗出嚟就拿柒佢，訓一晚第日會細粒啲，然後KEEP住漱口"},{"pid":"7afadd4004c5d96756adafb5aec308006399a5c5","tid":2097233,"uid":46275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"買支李斯德能浪口會唔會有效D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351fceb3d56b4ca7b456b1c2fc64625ee2aaf231","tid":2097233,"uid":359022,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"屈臣氏買bonjela<br />\n跟指引 每次用乾淨棉花棒 好快好<br />\n注意 小朋友唔可以用 佢有出小朋友版 但hk暫時未見過"},{"pid":"65481d75e63875f07f5e1d5b47969e51c24c8415","tid":2097233,"uid":55583,"li